<lb ed="I" n="0078b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0078b0101">大魏永安三年歲次庚戌七月甲戌十一日□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b02" type="honorific"/>夫大聖慈隆。演化脩導。善業顯彰。倉生咸慕。曠代遵
<lb ed="I" n="0078b03" type="honorific"/>崇。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078001" n="0078001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078001" n="0078001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078001" n="0078001"/>虛<anchor xml:id="end0078001"/>空无碍。雖<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078002" n="0078002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078002" n="0078002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078002" n="0078002"/>冥<anchor xml:id="end0078002"/>運不弔。真容凝位。是故
<lb ed="I" n="0078b04" type="honorific"/>釋□□生。以<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078003" n="0078003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078003" n="0078003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078003" n="0078003"/>啓<anchor xml:id="end0078003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078004" n="0078004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078004" n="0078004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078004" n="0078004"/>權<anchor xml:id="end0078004"/>曜。是以形教之興。敷沾有氣之
<lb ed="I" n="0078b05" type="honorific"/>□□□影念貌遺像。但雙等。規奉玄門。幼染繢服。
<lb ed="I" n="0078b06" type="honorific"/>□□□巖岳寄氣。松石自慨。剾□返掌蹉跌又□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b07" type="honorific"/>□□□命如朝露。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078005" n="0078005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078005" n="0078005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078005" n="0078005"/>仰<anchor xml:id="end0078005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078006" n="0078006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078006" n="0078006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078006" n="0078006"/>勸<anchor xml:id="end0078006"/>師僧同<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">學</unclear>　衣鉢
<lb ed="I" n="0078b08" type="honorific"/>□□□四背。減妻子之珍。分於末代□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b09" type="honorific"/>□□餘人。咸自開悟。建　釋迦石像
<lb ed="I" n="0078b10" type="honorific"/>□□薩兩師子。并天宮一區。起永安□
<lb ed="I" n="0078b11" type="honorific"/>功□□月十一日營訖。妙體沖邃。容貌澄相
<lb ed="I" n="0078b12" type="honorific"/>光曜　<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078007" n="0078007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078007" n="0078007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078007" n="0078007"/>邊<anchor xml:id="end0078007"/>外。<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>仰<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>為
<lb ed="I" n="0078b13" type="honorific"/>皇帝　陛下。群遼百<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078008" n="0078008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078008" n="0078008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078008" n="0078008"/>辟<anchor xml:id="end0078008"/>。中宮內外。師僧父母。因緣眷
<lb ed="I" n="0078b14" type="honorific"/>屬。善<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">友</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">知</unclear>識。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078009" n="0078009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078009" n="0078009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078009" n="0078009"/>逮<anchor xml:id="end0078009"/>及七世。一切无<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>邊<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>眾生。願沾　　速
<lb ed="I" n="0078b15" type="honorific"/>成正覺。□同斯福　　大像邑都唯那比丘道陰
<lb ed="I" n="0078b16" type="honorific"/>□□□大像邑主前廣業寺主比丘慧雙<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0078010" n="0078010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0078010" n="0078010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0078010" n="0078010"/>率<anchor xml:id="end0078010"/>造
<lb ed="I" n="0078b17" type="honorific"/>□□□□</p>
</cb:div>
